Program: Outlook
Title: Bombings in Dahab Resort
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrz6
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Eyewitness account of the bombing in Egyptian resort, Dahab. Also, dating in Iran. Afghan TV host Shakeb Isaar on fleeing Afghanistan when his co-host was murdered. The man in charge of one of Calcutta's last synagogues. Childhood obesity in Italy. Finally, Andy Ford on skydiving through clouds.